Class Player

java.lang.Object
edu.guilford.Player
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Player extends Object implements Serializable
This class is used to store the player data. It is used to store the player's statistics for a single year. The class also contains methods to get and set the player's data, as well as methods to get the attributes of the player class. The class also contains methods to get and set the player's data, as well as methods to get the attributes of the player class.
